WEBVTT

00:02.835 --> 00:07.741
Shri Saraswati Puja, Vancouver (Canada)
August 11th, 1990

00:25.200 --> 00:28.925
When they asked Me

00:32.149 --> 00:38.304
what puja we should have in Vancouver,

00:38.329 --> 00:45.997
I had heard about this ashram that
it is placed

00:46.022 --> 00:51.517
in very beautiful surroundings of nature

00:54.539 --> 01:04.246
and, as nature is being created by the
power of Saraswati,

01:04.271 --> 01:11.999
I thought best would be to have the Puja
of Saraswati here.

01:12.024 --> 01:16.526
Another thing is that when people live
in nature,

01:16.551 --> 01:26.665
they become extremely creative, their
delicate feelings are preserved

01:26.690 --> 01:36.147
and they are never in a rush; or they are
not what we can call too much modernized,

01:36.172 --> 01:40.590
because nature soothes them down.

01:40.615 --> 01:47.911
So also the creativity of Saraswati adds
to artist,

01:47.936 --> 01:56.227
and I knew that there must have been
many artist in this country created

01:56.252 --> 01:59.044
since long.

02:02.317 --> 02:13.844
The Canada as such I feel is the Hamsa
Chakra of the Vishuddhi,

02:13.869 --> 02:28.142
but the power of Saraswati becomes
Mahasaraswati

02:28.167 --> 02:38.122
when it is manifested by the Mahabrahmadeva
which is called as Hiranyagarbha.

02:38.147 --> 02:43.006
For that She has to cross through
the Hamsa.

02:43.031 --> 02:49.721
She crosses through Hamsa and becomes
the Vishnumaya Shakti.

02:52.701 --> 03:01.277
I mean She is the Vishnumaya Shakti.
So Saraswati becomes the Vishnumaya.

03:01.302 --> 03:05.209
She crosses at two points – one at Hamsa

03:05.234 --> 03:14.990
and another at Vishuddhi – so She is
the Sister of Shri Krishna.

03:15.015 --> 03:21.704
So Saraswati was born as the Sister
of Shri Krishna,

03:21.729 --> 03:30.210
and when Krishna’s mama, his name was,
his uncle was Kamsa,

03:30.235 --> 03:40.154
he came to kill Her, She just rose
into the sky and became the lightning,

03:40.154 --> 03:51.885
and She declared the coming of Shri
Krishna, that He is already there existing.

03:51.910 --> 03:56.090
So the relationship between Shri Krishna

03:56.115 --> 04:02.212
and Vishnumaya is that of a brother
and a sister,

04:02.237 --> 04:09.571
and surprisingly the other day we
celebrated the Rakhi Bandhan,

04:09.596 --> 04:15.990
Raksha Bandhan, which is the same thing
as the brothers/sisters relationship.

04:16.015 --> 04:21.284
So now here we are celebrating actually
the Deity which is the Sister

04:21.309 --> 04:27.929
of Shri Krishna. Later on She was born
as Draupadi,

04:27.954 --> 04:31.720
and that’s why Shri Krishna went to save
Her chastity,

04:31.745 --> 04:36.165
because is the brother only who is
concerned about the chastity

04:36.190 --> 04:40.279
and the name of the sister.

04:40.304 --> 04:48.168
So this is what yesterday happened
that is the Saraswati Puja,

04:48.193 --> 04:57.403
so Vishnumaya, Herself, yesterday
sixteen times thundered here;

04:57.428 --> 05:02.379
and I didn’t tell anybody what was
happening, but I knew She would do that.

05:02.404 --> 05:07.946
And apart from that, She has also
threatened Washington.

05:07.971 --> 05:12.808
That’s a good thing because Washington
has to be awakened.

05:12.833 --> 05:17.434
Now these are very, very subtle things
and very subtle relations,

05:17.459 --> 05:23.820
and only I can tell these things because
I know them,

05:23.820 --> 05:30.615
that these relations exist. So I was not
surprised that She was there,

05:30.640 --> 05:37.967
but exactly sixteen hundred times
She passed it, this part of Vancouver,

05:37.992 --> 05:47.376
is to show that the time has come for you
to understand

05:47.401 --> 05:51.318
that Sahaja Yoga is so important,

05:51.343 --> 05:57.239
and if we do not assert ourselves fully
to Sahaja Yoga,

05:57.264 --> 06:02.542
Vishnumaya is going to take another
form which may burn all your forest,

06:02.567 --> 06:07.649
may burn everything. Now you must know
that lightning represents

06:07.674 --> 06:13.429
all the five elements in it.

06:13.454 --> 06:19.669
It has sound, it has light, it is
in the ether, it acts in the ether.

06:19.694 --> 06:26.669
Also it has got what you called
the water in it,

06:26.694 --> 06:33.759
and when the water goes into friction,
which is the Mother Earth,

06:33.784 --> 06:37.730
so all these things act through Her.

06:37.755 --> 06:41.869
So this Vishnumaya yesterday showed us that

06:41.869 --> 06:50.331
“I’m here now. Please worship Me.” And
so far we have never worshiped Saraswati,

06:50.356 --> 06:54.716
and Brahmadeva is not worshiped anywhere
because He created this world,

06:54.741 --> 07:02.080
He created all these woods and all these
things and they created

07:02.105 --> 07:12.685
all the seas and all the lands,
all the stars, universes after universes.

07:12.710 --> 07:17.734
But we are not to worship like we worship
this tree or that tree.

07:17.759 --> 07:21.543
We are not to worship anything of that
kind, only thing

07:21.543 --> 07:27.154
whatever is created by Mother Earth like
Swayambus, that’s only we worship.

07:27.179 --> 07:31.648
And that, too, we worship now in a way
that is in an abstract way,

07:31.673 --> 07:37.031
because wherever they have appeared
people are doing commercial religion,

07:37.056 --> 07:42.132
so we don’t go to these places also
as sahaja yogis.

07:42.157 --> 07:44.902
So you can understand why all these
things happened

07:44.927 --> 07:48.402
unexpectedly yesterday after My coming,

07:48.427 --> 07:52.865
that there was such a light of lightning
which never happened before

07:52.890 --> 07:57.064
and people were surprised. So is
the Krishna’s Sister

07:57.089 --> 08:07.232
who is a much more dynamic and

08:10.711 --> 08:16.732
[Shri Mataji speaks aside in Hindi]

08:22.316 --> 08:26.913
much more fiery personality – much,
much more fiery personality.

08:26.938 --> 08:39.189
Shri Krishna’s essence is that He is
sweetness, is Madhuria is His capacity

08:39.214 --> 08:45.058
and Radha is the Allahda Dayini Shakti,
means the One which gives you

08:45.083 --> 08:50.587
that joy which creates

08:52.911 --> 08:55.437
[Shri Mataji speaks aside in Hindi],

08:55.462 --> 09:01.757
raises your hair with joy – so,
but in Sanskrit it is pulakit,

09:01.782 --> 09:10.084
pulakita is the word. So this beauty
of Shri Krishna which is sweetness,

09:10.109 --> 09:23.902
the leela, creating beautiful feelings
of oneness, of communication –

09:23.927 --> 09:28.249
all that is in Shri Krishna. But She’s
the One who warns,

09:28.274 --> 09:33.192
and that is how the warning came. And She’s
a very fiery personality

09:33.217 --> 09:39.436
which warns everyone. So on one way
She has proved My coming here,

09:39.461 --> 09:44.910
that I’m here. Perhaps maybe to the people
who are aboriginals they might understand

09:44.935 --> 09:49.508
that this is what was prophesied and that
has happened,

09:49.508 --> 09:54.928
and also that you people have to realize:
it’s a warning

09:54.953 --> 09:59.973
that you cannot just allow Sahaja Yoga
to drift in such a manner

09:59.973 --> 10:03.874
that it takes its own course and works out,

10:03.899 --> 10:08.118
and you are just by the way there.
So this is a warning

10:08.143 --> 10:12.484
of Shri Krishna’s Sister, Vishnumaya,
which is Saraswati Herself,

10:12.509 --> 10:17.368
and that is what today we are going
to worship Her. Only the sahaja yogis,

10:17.393 --> 10:22.675
those who are enlightened people,
can worship Mahasaraswati.

10:22.700 --> 10:28.259
Otherwise people can only worship Saraswati
because with worship of Saraswati

10:28.284 --> 10:36.944
you can read books, you can create
dances, music,

10:36.969 --> 10:42.134
for the amusement of human beings,
but actually the Saraswati Puja

10:42.159 --> 10:48.931
is meant for people of ordinary awareness,

10:48.956 --> 10:52.193
means ordinary or normal human awareness.

10:52.218 --> 10:59.267
But for sahaja yogis, it is the
Mahasaraswati which is to be worshiped.

10:59.292 --> 11:03.275
As I have told you this Mahasaraswati
becomes the Vishnumaya,

11:03.300 --> 11:10.818
and She is Vishnumaya so you have to be
person that you should,

11:10.843 --> 11:18.989
yourself should inform people like
the Vishnumaya does what Sahaja Yoga is

11:19.014 --> 11:23.694
with your fiery talks, with things
of exciting them,

11:23.719 --> 11:29.156
telling them what are you up to.
But what I have seen is that mostly

11:29.181 --> 11:36.306
when people speak they try to be very
gentle and sweet like Shri Krishna.

11:36.331 --> 11:39.555
We tried that in America, that it might
work with Americans,

11:39.580 --> 11:44.915
but it did not. They like people like say
that Graham fellow

11:44.940 --> 11:50.240
or somebody like that who talks in a fiery
way. And I think this is what we have

11:50.265 --> 11:55.840
to learn from yesterday’s experience:
that you need really some fiery speakers

11:55.865 --> 12:01.206
and fiery people because they are not
at all sensitive

12:01.231 --> 12:07.752
to normal sensations. You see they,
all their sensations are dead I think

12:07.777 --> 12:12.703
they have become numb, and you have
to give them some shocks.

12:12.728 --> 12:16.728
They like shocks, you see. Newspapers
have to give them shocks,

12:16.753 --> 12:21.743
any event that is shocking – that can
only attract their attention.

12:21.768 --> 12:25.285
Even the music has to be so much
that it should break the rocks.

12:25.310 --> 12:29.678
So it should be such music that will just
break their heads.

12:29.703 --> 12:33.968
So they have become really rocky people,
and you have to

12:33.993 --> 12:38.357
understand that their rockiness can only
be shattered by Vishnumaya.

12:38.382 --> 12:42.167
And that’s why this puja that we have
today in Vancouver

12:42.192 --> 12:49.382
has a very great significance – not only
for Canada, but also for America.

12:49.407 --> 12:54.696
Americans are taking for granted whatever
diseases coming today,

12:54.721 --> 12:58.166
whatever drugs they are taking, whatever
destruction they’re doing

12:58.191 --> 13:04.158
to themselves is still not in their
understanding.

13:04.183 --> 13:06.368
They don’t understand what they’re doing
to themselves,

13:06.393 --> 13:08.017
how they’re destroying themselves,

13:08.042 --> 13:13.316
how such a precious human life they’re
wasting just for their own whim

13:13.341 --> 13:19.050
and for their so-called freedom. So it is
extremely, extremely important

13:19.075 --> 13:24.962
that you should try to tell them
in a fiery way, “What are you doing?

13:24.987 --> 13:28.981
Why are you deceiving yourself? Why don’t
you understand this is wrong?

13:29.006 --> 13:32.998
At least for the progeny, you tell them
that ‘We did this wrong,

13:33.023 --> 13:38.600
but you should not do it.'”All this kind
of talk has to be there

13:38.625 --> 13:44.200
and people have to get ready for such
great speeches and things,

13:44.225 --> 13:51.685
but to say that people won’t like it,
I think is the other way round,

13:51.710 --> 13:56.042
unless and until you frighten them
they’re not going to be with you.

13:56.067 --> 13:58.546
So you have to tell and warn them

13:58.546 --> 14:01.621
and that’s what the Vishnumaya yesterday
has suggested

14:01.646 --> 14:04.363
that now take to a new style of strategy

14:04.388 --> 14:09.557
and talk to people in a way that whenever
you are doing - say you are doing a course,

14:09.582 --> 14:13.414
at the end of the course you have to say
that “Now, see, Sahaja Yoga is not for only

14:13.439 --> 14:18.050
for doing course, but it’s for your
well being, for your benevolence.

14:18.075 --> 14:22.368
And you have to go further with it and you
have to grow. Now don’t leave it half way.”

14:22.393 --> 14:24.974
It’s not like just sprouting the seed,
but it has

14:24.999 --> 14:28.963
to become the tree otherwise nobody
can be helped.

14:28.988 --> 14:37.940
So you see just tell them they – all the
dangers of not being properly brought up

14:37.965 --> 14:41.968
or matured in Sahaja Yoga. It has to be told

14:41.993 --> 14:46.391
because all this lovey-dovey business
doesn’t help in America, I’ve seen that.

14:46.416 --> 14:51.808
You need really fiery people because
recently I was listening to a speech

14:51.833 --> 14:56.271
of this Billy Graham, and I said,
“It’s such an empty-headed fellow

14:56.296 --> 15:01.315
talks through his hat,” but still people
were so impressed.

15:01.340 --> 15:04.530
And there was another one now I think
he is behind jail.

15:04.555 --> 15:10.097
I don’t know his name, some funny man.
So I saw him also,

15:10.122 --> 15:15.220
I was surprised he was just talking
something empty, like empty shell

15:15.245 --> 15:18.699
and people were all mad after him
– thousands standing,

15:18.724 --> 15:21.317
singing, doing this, doing that.

15:21.342 --> 15:24.785
So one has to understand that these
people require shocks,

15:24.810 --> 15:28.912
and they’re to be shocked and they’re
to be told that “This is going to happen.”

15:28.937 --> 15:37.776
There’s one other organisation which has
gone into a kind of a shocking system

15:43.357 --> 15:48.328
is the [Shri Mataji speaks aside in Hindi]

15:50.039 --> 15:54.544
Brahma Kumari, Brahma Kumari, you see
these Brahma Kumaris

15:54.569 --> 15:57.692
have become like lightnings and they
tell people –

15:57.717 --> 16:00.946
now they don’t tell that, “You are
destroyed,” what they tell,

16:00.971 --> 16:04.565
“This world is going to be destroyed,
everything is going to be destroyed

16:04.590 --> 16:08.408
and you know you are not prepared for it,
what’s going to happen?”

16:08.433 --> 16:11.864
Same thing Jehovah Witness is doing,
the same thing. They are saying,

16:11.889 --> 16:16.809
“This world is going to be destroyed,
and we are all going to be destroyed;

16:16.834 --> 16:23.172
so we should be prepared and we should
take to God.”

16:23.663 --> 16:28.136
But this is not reality. Despite that
people are after them.

16:28.161 --> 16:35.520
You have to tell them the reality that
“Not only that you’re destroying yourself,

16:35.545 --> 16:39.887
but you’re destroying the future.”
People are already talking

16:39.912 --> 16:44.685
that most of the people in America
will be destroyed.

16:44.710 --> 16:50.249
Now it comes from various reasons. We can
say that there are no traditions and things

16:50.249 --> 16:52.900
– that’s not the point, that’s not
the main point.

16:52.925 --> 16:56.039
One of the main points is that they
destroyed so many people

16:56.064 --> 17:00.872
when they came and settled down in this
country. That’s one point.

17:00.897 --> 17:07.139
Now the bhoots of those people who died
are still hanging around,

17:07.164 --> 17:12.389
and they want to see that they destroy
Americans as far as possible.

17:12.414 --> 17:17.426
The amount of witchcraft, the amount
of all negative techniques

17:17.451 --> 17:21.124
that are working in America, they’re
working nowhere.

17:21.149 --> 17:25.037
The gurus had to get out of
all the countries,

17:25.062 --> 17:28.447
but they’re still very nicely settled
in America.

17:28.472 --> 17:33.303
The reason is these bhoots are giving
them ideas. It’s not only that

17:33.328 --> 17:36.183
they need shocks, but also these bhoots
give them

17:36.208 --> 17:41.416
these perverted ideas of destruction,
so they go for their destruction.

17:41.441 --> 17:48.166
Now the bhootish ideas are such that
you see a person coming out of a pub,

17:48.191 --> 17:52.157
falls down. And a bhootish idea is that
“What’s the harm?

17:52.182 --> 17:55.667
You also try, you will never fall.
You go in, nothing will happen to you.

17:55.692 --> 17:59.961
You’re perfectly all right. After all,
doesn’t matter.”

17:59.986 --> 18:05.780
Or else you tell them that “This is wrong.
We should not do.”

18:05.805 --> 18:11.533
“All right, so we are bad. So what?”
These are all bhootish ideas.

18:11.558 --> 18:15.506
These are not human ideas to talk
like this or to say like that.

18:15.531 --> 18:22.161
So to all these people, you see, the only
thing that is going to bring round

18:22.186 --> 18:25.192
is the Vishnumaya Shakti, nothing else.

18:25.217 --> 18:29.770
I now realize that it’s only through
Vishnumaya people can be cured.

18:29.795 --> 18:36.317
So Vishnumaya Itself now has gone off
to sleep, thanks to Christian religion,

18:36.342 --> 18:40.186
Catholic religion and also Hinduism,
because in Hinduism also

18:40.211 --> 18:44.656
there is a idea of sin – that you have
sinned this, you have done that sin.

18:44.681 --> 18:47.928
So you give so much money to the Brahmin,
so you’ll be saved.

18:47.953 --> 18:50.487
I mean every religion has this nonsense.

18:50.512 --> 18:53.613
But this Vishnumaya Shakti, which is
being absolutely

18:53.638 --> 18:58.720
subdued and is sleeping in human beings,
if you can raise it and tell people

18:58.745 --> 19:03.847
to get up out of this slumber,
this laziness,

19:03.871 --> 19:11.454
by involving them very much in a bigger
way, by telling them that we are for peace,

19:11.479 --> 19:16.270
peace of the world. We are for
the emancipation of the humanity,

19:16.295 --> 19:22.564
we are for saving people from blunders
and from their destruction.

19:22.589 --> 19:30.188
If you take a bigger platform and talk
about those things, then it will be helped.

19:30.213 --> 19:35.234
For example, now it’s a very good thing
that I was with Mahatma Gandhi,

19:35.259 --> 19:39.931
and people have got great respect
for Mahatma Gandhi.

19:39.956 --> 19:43.371
Of course and Mahatma Gandhi was very much
impressed about Me, no doubt.

19:43.396 --> 19:50.158
Even when I was a child, he used to consult
Me, and the proof of that is

19:50.183 --> 19:59.473
that in his bhajans he has put the serial
of the bhajans in different ways,

19:59.498 --> 20:04.711
starting from the heart, talking about
the Atma and then he’s starting

20:04.736 --> 20:10.185
from the Mooladhara upward, like that.

20:10.210 --> 20:16.375
So I mean that’s one of the proofs
that he must have consulted Me.

20:16.400 --> 20:22.868
But whatever it is, you have – can use
him also that Shri Mataji is doing

20:22.893 --> 20:28.188
what Mahatma Gandhi said. He has
talked about sarva dharma savanatma

20:28.213 --> 20:33.168
means all the religions are treated with
same respect and same understanding.

20:33.193 --> 20:36.782
Once you start talking like that, you see,
then people will understand

20:36.807 --> 20:41.032
that it has some noble heritage behind it,
because everybody wants to know

20:41.057 --> 20:44.454
from what book I’ve learnt. I mean,
I have never learnt from any book,

20:44.479 --> 20:48.707
that you know very well. But you can say
that “She is the One who was with him”

20:48.732 --> 20:51.474
and that “He was very much impressed
by Her,”

20:51.499 --> 20:55.114
and the same ideas of peace and non
violence and all that.

20:55.139 --> 20:58.943
“These are the same techniques
and methods She wants to use.”

20:58.968 --> 21:03.467
That’s a fact, no doubt, but Mahatma
Gandhi was a very fiery speaker.

21:03.492 --> 21:07.242
All people who followed him were
very fiery.

21:07.267 --> 21:11.197
They were not just “All right, come along,
have a cup of tea”

21:11.222 --> 21:15.688
and this kind of thing is not going
to work out.

21:15.713 --> 21:22.900
So Americans need challenge, and they need
really a fiery person to blast them.

21:22.925 --> 21:26.460
So now if you go on this way –

21:26.485 --> 21:29.885
like the other day when we had a program
in New York

21:29.910 --> 21:37.639
and there were so many black people
and so many Chinese,

21:37.664 --> 21:42.733
and then there were so many Indians
and very few were whites.

21:42.758 --> 21:46.782
So whites came and say, “Oh, nothing
has happened to me, you know.”

21:46.807 --> 21:49.635
