got it? Oh, it’s very wrong,

22:03.964 --> 22:06.576
something wrong with you. You should
get it. Try to get it, you know,

22:06.601 --> 22:11.629
it’s very wrong. I hope you don’t have
cancer.” Then...

22:17.362 --> 22:20.358
