from AIDS?” “No, no, no.”

22:20.354 --> 22:23.217
“Then what are you suffering from? How is
it you didn’t get it? You see

22:23.242 --> 22:28.012
this black man got it, this Chinese
has got it. Why don’t you get it?

22:28.037 --> 22:33.097
You are a white skin man, you should
get it first.”

22:36.226 --> 22:40.141
Then things will work out. I have been
thinking about it, why these Americans

22:40.166 --> 22:45.444
are so dull, because you see they are
on the whole very dull people,

22:45.469 --> 22:49.205
extremely dull. Because this kind of a rock
music, you see, if you play

22:49.230 --> 22:53.163
before anyone people would run away.
“What is this going on?”

22:53.188 --> 22:57.684
But the way they like this rap music
yesterday, they wanted Me to listen.

