And the whole thing started shaking.
I sat on a bench

23:03.982 --> 23:05.892
and the whole bench was shaking.

23:05.917 --> 23:12.235
There, who sat with Me was, he was there
and also Karan was there

23:12.260 --> 23:18.621
and we found that he – Karan and everybody
