“Come and hit me,” sort of thing, you see.
They have gone out of the way

23:41.879 --> 23:45.476
to numb themselves completely;
and this numbness may be

23:45.476 --> 23:50.051
alcohol, may be drugs, may be woman,
may be marrying so many times.

23:50.076 --> 23:57.184
If you marry one time, it’s sufficient.
If you marry five times, I mean you become

23:57.209 --> 24:04.039
– I don’t know what, like a – I don’t know
if there’s any animal like that.

24:04.064 --> 24:07.648
But something you become absolutely
numb to things, you see.

24:07.673 --> 24:10.662
Because first of all marrying one wife,

24:10.687 --> 24:15.274
then you have attachments with her,
you have children and you – I mean

24:15.299 --> 24:18.948
after all, it’s so much to do with
your wife

24:18.948 --> 24:24.705
and then suddenly you divorce and you
don’t feel anything, you don’t feel it.

24:24.730 --> 24:30.491
It’s great numbness and if you tell them,
“Yes, I know, I know, I know.”

24:30.516 --> 24:35.693
They know but they don’t feel. They don’t
feel that they’re doing anything wrong,

24:35.718 --> 24:40.732
they don’t feel they have done anything
absurd and they don’t suffer.

24:40.757 --> 24:45.701
Any other person would suffer. He has,
he has divorced his wife

24:45.726 --> 24:52.768
and it becomes really a person quite lost,
should be normally.

24:52.793 --> 24:57.655
But here what you find very nicely
boasting, “You know,

24:57.680 --> 25:04.616
I have divorced my two wives, and this
third one is coming up. You can meet her.”

25:04.641 --> 25:09.964
So that there’s no shame about it,
no shame, no feelings, nothing.

25:09.989 --> 25:13.272
I mean you married a woman, you lived
with her, she was your wife

25:13.297 --> 25:16.321
and you have no feelings for her.
Your own children also

25:16.346 --> 25:21.111
they have no feelings at all, no feelings.
Of course they’re not like English,

25:21.136 --> 25:24.471
where the English people kill their
children, so that’s not so bad.

25:24.496 --> 25:28.481
But here I’ve heard also that they kill
husband, wife, kills each other

25:28.506 --> 25:33.233
and all that. And for what? For love. When
they do not have love for one husband,

25:33.258 --> 25:36.603
how are they going to have love for
another husband? I can’t understand.

25:36.628 --> 25:38.480
Love is a quality of heart.

25:38.505 --> 25:43.783
So this is what it is – if you see
the whole character is numbed out

25:43.808 --> 25:46.774
because they don’t behave like human
beings.

25:46.799 --> 25:50.596
They behave like – I don’t know, again
I say I don’t know like whom

25:50.621 --> 25:52.735
because there’s no comparison
whatsoever.

25:52.760 --> 25:57.995
So it is not that only in America people
are like that, it's all over.

25:58.020 --> 26:04.487
But in America it is too much, too much of
it, and all such things rise from America.

26:04.512 --> 26:10.084
All such funny notions rise from America,
and everybody takes them

26:10.109 --> 26:20.544
because they know how to advertise, they
know how to make it very, very popular.

26:20.569 --> 26:26.373
Once I was travelling by a ship

26:26.398 --> 26:29.530
and a pilot came over the ship,
and he was talking to Me

26:29.555 --> 26:33.920
and he told Me that his brother is
a very nasty devil.

26:33.920 --> 26:38.612
I said, “What happened?” So he said
that he got hold of

26:38.637 --> 26:43.017
these four boys who were Beatles,
and he became their manager.

26:43.042 --> 26:47.828
And he started this music and got
some women,

26:47.853 --> 26:50.455
got them drunk, put them on drugs.

26:50.480 --> 26:54.300
And the first music when they had
that music,

26:54.325 --> 26:58.037
these girls started screaming, shouting,
going mad.

26:58.062 --> 27:02.116
And it became popular. Normally
the reaction would be that,

27:02.141 --> 27:06.559
“Ba, it’s such a thing that when the music
starts the girls go mad,

27:06.584 --> 27:10.814
so don’t go to such a music.” On the
contrary, so many started coming.

27:10.839 --> 27:15.435
How do you explain this kind of a reaction?
The more they shout, the more they scream,

27:15.460 --> 27:20.901
according to them it’s something.
Means behind it

27:20.926 --> 27:28.279
is one thing that it has touched them
somehow; otherwise, why will they scream?

27:28.304 --> 27:33.403
Means such dumb people have been touched
by something is something great

27:33.428 --> 27:39.584
and all of us should go. We are also dumb,
so we should attend to it.

27:39.609 --> 27:47.530
Now you may ask Me that “Mother how this
dumbness has come into people and this?”

27:47.530 --> 27:51.561
Is as simple as that as I told you,
that they’ve used their freedom

27:51.586 --> 27:56.817
to such an extent, their attention to such
a wasteful pursuits,

27:56.842 --> 28:00.553
that they have become really numb.
Their attention doesn’t feel anything.

28:00.578 --> 28:06.771
Attention when you put it out it reacts,
and it comes back to you as something.

28:06.796 --> 28:11.022
But if you all the time go on bombarding
outside your attention,

28:11.047 --> 28:15.479
this some bombardment from outside
just finishes all your sensitivity.

28:15.504 --> 28:20.000
There’s no feeling, there’s no attachment,

28:20.025 --> 28:27.540
there is no, no recording of anything
that is happening.

28:27.565 --> 28:30.434
So for that I think Vishnumaya is needed,

28:30.459 --> 28:34.797
and that’s why She’s placed on the left
side because Vishnumaya

28:34.822 --> 28:40.365
is the One in charge of people who have
become absolutely feelingless.

28:40.390 --> 28:42.849
That’s why She’s there to give you
the feeling.

28:42.874 --> 28:46.993
So on the left side when She shines
She gives you the feelings,

28:47.018 --> 28:51.747
and people start understanding. So now
the only thing that they have is

28:51.772 --> 28:57.556
a kind of a mental idea that they’re
guilty, that’s all.

28:57.581 --> 29:02.094
This is just mental. If it is mental idea,
“Oh, I’m guilty,”

29:02.119 --> 29:07.188
then you are not going to feel it. I mean
if you are, say that you are mad,

29:07.212 --> 29:11.929
when you’re not mad if anybody calls you
mad you are not going to feel it.

29:11.954 --> 29:14.757
It’s like this. So they don’t feel it
at all

29:14.782 --> 29:19.604
because it is all mentally accepted thing
and they have become numb,

29:19.629 --> 29:24.640
“Now nobody can harm you, so what’s wrong?”
sort of an attitude.

29:24.640 --> 29:29.508
I would now ask you people to go all out
and become fiery,

29:29.533 --> 29:33.951
write in newspapers and say what’s
happening and how things are.

29:33.976 --> 29:38.316
I’m writing a book like that now.
It’s called as Meta Modernism,

29:38.341 --> 29:43.218
and as far as I could be fiery I’m going
to be there

29:43.243 --> 29:46.394
to tell them what’s wrong with them.
And they should see to it

29:46.419 --> 29:53.968
that this is all wrong. No use trying
to call it something great.

29:53.993 --> 29:57.735
Like now AIDS have come up. I thought
with AIDS, they will be awakened.

29:57.760 --> 30:00.365
So now the AIDS have become a martyrdom.

30:00.390 --> 30:03.136
Now the yuppies, the yuppies came up,
I said,

30:03.161 --> 30:07.202
“The yuppies will suffer from a disease.”
So now they said,

30:07.227 --> 30:10.180
“No, no, no, no. It’s very nice to be
yuppies. After all you see

30:10.180 --> 30:14.277
they are another heroes who died
for their yuppism.”

30:14.302 --> 30:19.072
Like you see, every stupidity is made
into a something,

30:19.097 --> 30:22.633
kind of a very glorifying thing,

30:22.658 --> 30:28.840
so just – and people accept it. That’s
the best part of it – they accept it.

30:28.840 --> 30:32.521
So it is important for you to be fiery,
and to show them

30:32.546 --> 30:35.558
in that light what they are. They have
to be shown.

30:35.583 --> 30:40.580
It’s not just a little light of the Spirit
will show them much,

30:40.605 --> 30:49.981
but it’s the real dazzling, burning light
of a lightning.

30:50.006 --> 30:53.368
So today’s puja is going to be specially

30:53.393 --> 31:00.002
for you all to develop that creativity
of talking,

31:00.027 --> 31:03.470
behaving in every way in a fiery way.

31:03.495 --> 31:07.756
That is going to put them right,
nothing else.

31:07.781 --> 31:10.953
In creative work also, when we create
something

31:10.978 --> 31:14.191
or we sing something and all that,

31:14.216 --> 31:20.047
if you go on singing, say, in our Indian
style, some music which is

31:20.072 --> 31:23.871
“vilambit tala” you see, very slow “talas”,
that won’t come up.

31:23.896 --> 31:28.230
They like somebody like Ravi Shankar
who just goes on mixing up notes

31:28.255 --> 31:33.735
and just goes on playing something which
is very, very unscientific

31:33.760 --> 31:38.534
according to Indians things, is not at all
entertaining, it doesn’t open your heart

31:38.559 --> 31:42.784
and something like that. But, that is
the thing that appeals to them,

31:42.804 --> 31:49.376
to go into a big sort of a rock and roll
sort – make it, sitar

31:49.401 --> 31:53.200
into rock and roll, and even worse than
that. I don’t know the new, latest one

31:53.225 --> 31:57.795
I don’t know what it is. So the second
thing is that you can see

31:57.820 --> 32:02.134
how they try to shock people. Also they
try to shock people,

32:02.159 --> 32:06.080
because they know that they are also
like us. Like you go in the market,

32:06.105 --> 32:11.552
you find somebody, his pant is – not pant
even, half pant –

32:11.577 --> 32:18.055
is all torn at wrong places, and it is
just to shock people.

32:18.930 --> 32:22.179
They are supposed to, here at least,
they are supposed to,

32:22.204 --> 32:25.489
in America it is supposed to be, you have
to dress up

32:25.514 --> 32:28.479
decently. You should not be indecently
dressed.

32:28.504 --> 32:33.018
That’s what they want. But, what you find,
whatever chance they can get

32:33.043 --> 32:37.206
to dress up in a way that you’ll be
shocked, they would like to do.

32:37.231 --> 32:40.814
Like they’ll have only one part
of the hair as white.

32:40.839 --> 32:44.412
I mean anything, anything is possible
just to shock others,

32:44.437 --> 32:49.935
shock others and attract the attention.
And what do you get? Nothing.

32:49.960 --> 32:53.810
You spend so much money to attract the
attention of others, but what do you get?

32:53.835 --> 32:56.992
That attention doesn’t give you anything,
doesn’t pay you anything,

32:57.017 --> 33:02.079
doesn’t compensate. So it’s such
a joyless pursuit they get into.

33:02.104 --> 33:06.641
All these things spoil their attention,
which destroys it to this extent

33:06.666 --> 33:11.412
that they’re feelingless people.
They have no feelings left.

33:11.437 --> 33:15.179
And then the worse thing that has
happened is they have become

33:15.179 --> 33:18.889
absolutely money-orientated.

33:20.154 --> 33:25.428
So the money is another side of Saraswati.

33:25.453 --> 33:33.254
Saraswati is different from Lakshmi,

33:33.279 --> 33:38.432
so the Lakshmi and Saraswati never go
hand in hand.

33:38.457 --> 33:42.766
This is the reason why when they get
after Lakshmi,

33:42.791 --> 33:47.071
run after money too much, they get shocks.

33:47.096 --> 33:50.994
Because there’s a – suddenly you find
the stock exchange has fallen,

33:51.019 --> 33:55.346
there’s a recession, this business is gone,
somebody who’s very rich

33:55.371 --> 34:00.050
suddenly becomes a poor man.
Is all the work,

34:00.075 --> 34:04.417
this is all the work of the Saraswati.

34:04.442 --> 34:09.846
And if somebody is too much in Saraswati
– reads too many books,

34:09.871 --> 34:14.891
is an artist who is very ambitious,

34:14.916 --> 34:18.837
who tries to outshine other artist
and all that –

34:18.862 --> 34:23.427
such a person also gets back a reward
from Lakshmi

34:23.452 --> 34:27.336
that his things never sell, he never gets
money, he starves,

34:27.361 --> 34:33.919
all sorts of thing. So these two things
are in balance only in Hamsa,

34:33.944 --> 34:38.504
or we can say they are in balance
when you are a sahaja yogi.

34:38.529 --> 34:45.472
So this has to be achieved and is to be
put together in balance

34:45.497 --> 34:51.479
that you have the blessings of
Saraswati as well as that of Lakshmi.

34:51.504 --> 34:56.785
But it crosses only at the Hamsa point
and at the Vishuddhi point.

34:56.810 --> 35:03.054
So what we have to do to bring
the balance is that whatever

35:03.079 --> 35:08.753
we are earning, whatever we are doing,
we should not be in a mediocre way.

35:08.778 --> 35:15.253
We should try to do it in a dynamic way,
in a fiery way.

35:15.688 --> 35:20.003
These two things should be combined
at the Vishuddhi level.

35:20.028 --> 35:29.602
So now, supposing you are going to give
a lecture about Sahaja Yoga in a fiery way,

35:29.627 --> 35:35.500
and if you wear a dress that you look like
a hippie or somebody coming out of a jail,

35:35.500 --> 35:39.574
nobody is going to take you seriously.
But if you’re properly dressed

35:39.599 --> 35:43.391
and you look respectable and presentation
is good,

35:43.416 --> 35:48.261
and then you give a fiery speech,
everybody is going to listen.

35:48.286 --> 35:55.597
So this principle of Lakshmi Tattwa
is to be used

35:55.622 --> 35:59.534
with the domination of the Saraswati
principle.

35:59.559 --> 36:08.518
Now another blessings of Saraswati is that
you can have knowledge of Sahaja Yoga.

36:08.543 --> 36:13.485
I’ve seen many women especially
in Sahaja Yoga,

36:14.473 --> 36:18.301
they’re sahaja yogis, they have vibrations,
all that is there,

36:18.326 --> 36:23.216
but they do not know what is Sahaja Yoga.

36:23.241 --> 36:28.054
They do not know what these chakras are.

36:28.054 --> 36:32.457
They do not know that how these vibrations
go out.

36:32.482 --> 36:37.791
Now today’s lecture is quite a lecture
quite complicated I would say,

36:37.816 --> 36:42.530
if you see to it. You have to listen to it
at least four, five times to understand it

36:42.555 --> 36:45.780
with the paper and a pencil. It’s not
an easy thing

36:45.805 --> 36:48.667
because I’m telling you now it’s all right,
it’s quite entertaining,

36:48.692 --> 36:53.595
but behind the entertainment there is
a deep knowledge.

36:53.620 --> 36:59.513
So I’ve not seen the sahaja yoginis
mostly sit down with a paper and pencil

36:59.538 --> 37:03.768
to know what is Mother saying,

37:03.793 --> 37:07.814
what is the knowledge She’s giving us
about the various things.

37:07.839 --> 37:14.545
To them Sahaja Yoga means to be nice,
to cook good food

37:14.570 --> 37:21.660
and help the sahaja yogis, and that
of course for the pujas to wear nice saris

37:21.685 --> 37:28.345
and nice dresses, come to the pujas
and all that and finished, also.

37:28.370 --> 37:34.272
So for them it is very important that they
should also know what is Sahaja Yoga.

37:34.297 --> 37:39.706
They must listen to My lectures, sit down,
study it nicely and understand it.

37:39.731 --> 37:45.694
The other way round are the men.
For them it is to do all the outside work,

37:45.719 --> 37:55.438
go round, see things and all that. But
as far as relationships are concerned,

37:55.463 --> 38:00.981
or as far as emotional side are concerned,
they’re negligent.

38:01.006 --> 38:04.362
And that is why Sahaja Yoga by men
is different;

38:04.387 --> 38:06.588
Sahaja Yoga by women is different.

38:06.613 --> 38:11.511
And in France specially it has gone
very far away from each other.

38:11.536 --> 38:14.186
The women were on one side, man are
on other side.

38:14.211 --> 38:17.974
Imagine in Sahaja Yoga you have such
a nonsense as that,

38:17.999 --> 38:21.636
but then we discovered the person who
was doing it and we managed it,

38:21.661 --> 38:24.346
so it was settled down and now things
are better.

38:24.371 --> 38:29.373
But women must know about Sahaja Yoga,
but that doesn’t mean

38:29.398 --> 38:32.944
that they should fight with them, or think
that they also know

38:32.969 --> 38:38.967
what these men know. But it’s very,
very common. I’ve seen that men

38:38.992 --> 38:43.945
and women are having a different type
of attitude towards Sahaja Yoga.

38:43.970 --> 38:47.085
One is an extravert, another is
an introvert.

38:47.110 --> 38:51.212
But in Sahaja Yoga there is no difference
between a woman and a man

38:51.237 --> 38:55.733
as far as knowing Sahaja Yoga is concerned.
I’m a woman Myself

38:55.758 --> 39:00.786
and I know so much, so why not the woman
shouldn’t know about what is Sahaja Yoga?

39:00.811 --> 39:06.630
So all the women who are here or all over
have to know what is Sahaja Yoga.

39:06.655 --> 39:13.493
After all, look at Vishnumaya – She is
a woman, is the Power that works.

39:13.518 --> 39:16.923
Brahmadeva doesn’t work. He’s created
all these things because

39:16.948 --> 39:21.346
He has the Power of Saraswati, otherwise
He could not have created.

39:21.371 --> 39:24.964
So everything is done through the Power
and the Power is a woman,

39:24.989 --> 39:27.219
but if the Power doesn’t know what is
Sahaja Yoga,

39:27.244 --> 39:31.043
how is She going to work it out?

39:31.490 --> 39:34.031
So the women, though they have children,
I know –

39:34.056 --> 39:38.600
they have to look after the household,
kitchen – but it’s such a pleasure,

39:38.625 --> 39:43.820
such a joy to read about Sahaja Yoga,
to understand it, to know it.

39:43.845 --> 39:48.725
Of course some of them do also read.
I’m not saying that they do not.

39:48.750 --> 39:53.874
But there are very, very few and they
are very sensible, very sensible.

39:53.899 --> 40:01.310
So this is My understanding of today’s
happening that in this natural surrounding,

40:01.335 --> 40:07.804
these natural surrounding where we are
blessed by the work of Brahmadeva

40:07.829 --> 40:15.409
and Saraswati, and where we can feel
the capacity of these Deities,

40:15.434 --> 40:22.011
to what extent They can create.
The nature is absolutely one

40:22.036 --> 40:28.477
with the Divine. Now see, as soon as
I came here the nature knew I’m there.

40:28.502 --> 40:32.189
It just started acting by itself. I didn’t
have to give them a lecture,

40:32.214 --> 40:35.159
they didn’t have to do a puja, nothing
of the kind.

40:35.184 --> 40:38.445
They knew what I was doing. I went
to Los Angeles, same thing.

40:38.470 --> 40:41.667
Anywhere I go the nature knows what is
to be done,

40:41.692 --> 40:47.160
“Now Mother is in the town, what should
we do?” And they do it.

40:47.185 --> 40:52.602
So this is the trouble, is that I have made
you to do all kinds of deliberations

40:52.627 --> 40:56.581
for human beings that “All right, do this,
do that, do that.”

40:56.606 --> 41:01.474
But I would say that spontaneously it
should act, because now we are one.

41:01.499 --> 41:04.743
Just like the nature is one with Me,
you are also one with Me.

41:04.768 --> 41:12.135
And that should start happening when
you will really become absolutely

41:12.174 --> 41:18.490
drawn into Sahaja Yoga, surrendered into
Sahaja Yoga, then only it will happen.

41:18.515 --> 41:21.563
May God bless you all.
